#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.log_expit.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.log\\_expit"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:1 of
msgid "Logarithm of the logistic sigmoid function."
msgstr "逻辑 sigmoid 函数的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:3 of
msgid ""
"The SciPy implementation of the logistic sigmoid function is "
"`scipy.special.expit`, so this function is called ``log_expit``."
msgstr ""
"逻辑 sigmoid 函数的 SciPy 实现是 `scipy.special.expit`，因此该函数称为 ``"
"log_expit``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:6 of
msgid ""
"The function is mathematically equivalent to ``log(expit(x))``, but is "
"formulated to avoid loss of precision for inputs with large (positive or "
"negative) magnitude."
msgstr ""
"该函数在数学上等价于 ``log(expit(x))``，但其公式设计避免了输入值较大（正"
"或负）时的精度损失。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:10 of
msgid "The values to apply ``log_expit`` to element-wise."
msgstr "要对其逐元素应用 ``log_expit`` 的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:12 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "函数结果的可选输出数组"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:15 of
msgid "**out** -- The computed values, an ndarray of the same shape as ``x``."
msgstr "**out** -- 计算结果，一个与 ``x`` 形状相同的 ndarray。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`expit`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.log_expit:22 of
msgid ""
"As a ufunc, ``log_expit`` takes a number of optional keyword arguments. "
"For more information see `ufuncs "
"<https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/ufuncs.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"作为一个 ufunc，``log_expit`` 接受多个可选关键字参数。更多信息请参见 `"
"ufuncs <https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/ufuncs.html>`_"

